@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14

title RIP: loop si count-to-infinity (concept)

[Router R1] as R1
[Router R2] as R2
[Router R3] as R3
[Retea Z] as Z

R1 -- R2
R2 -- R3
R3 -- R1
R1 -- Z

note right of R2
  Daca legatura R1-Z cade,
  R2 poate "invata" fals de la R3
  ca Z e accesibila prin R1,
  iar metrica creste treptat (pana la 16).
end note

note bottom
  Mitigari RIP:
  split horizon, route poisoning, holddown, timeout.
end note
@enduml
